Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Melvin Belli (1907-1996)
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjvq3
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 12 Jul 1996
A reflection on the life and legal crusade of the flamboyant US celebrity lawyer Melvin Belli, self-proclaimed defender of the 'little helpless guy'.